                    Compare Reviews for Automated Investment Services
                
            Automated investment services are designed to provide investors with low-fee investment management, using research supported investment strategies to create diversified passive investment portfolios for consumers.Automated investment services are a cross between a do-it-yourself approach and a higher paid financial advisor. Several robo-advisors also provide access to financial advisors for their users. These newer financial management platforms are ideal for investors seeking low fee investment management.
                        
